\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 STEP 2
\f1\b0\fs27 For the fricass\'e9e, heat the oil in a saut\'e9 pan, add the chorizo and fry for 2 mins until it starts to crisp and render out red oil. Throw the potatoes and paprika in the pan and cook for 5 mins, tossing occasionally, until they start to brown on the edges.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 
\fs36 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls1\ilvl0
