\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 STEP 3
\f1\b0\fs27 Pour in the chicken stock, turn up the heat and boil the stock for 8-10 mins until it has nearly all evaporated and the potatoes are tender. Stir the peas into the potatoes and cook for 2 mins more until heated through, then set aside.\cb1 \uc0\u8232 
\fs36 \uc0\u8232 \
